---

<div class="lead-magnet-container">
    <div class="lead-magnet-card">
        <h2>ðŸ“š Download Your Free Guide!</h2>
        <p>Enter your email below to get instant access to our **"Top 5 Tips for Building Local Websites"** guide.</p>
        
